<h6>16. Fee Policy</h6>

<ul>
	<li>Conditions The charges for rental of a vehicle will apply on an hourly basis. One hour will be considered complete if the time is in between 0 to 59 minutes. Accordingly, rental charges will apply for the vehicle. For instance, a user books the car for 5 hours and 20 minutes, the duration of the rental will be taken as 6 hours in total.</li>
</ul>

