	<li>In case a user is found drunk or under the usage of any illegal substance at the time of drop, a fine of INR 1000 will be levied. The cost of any sort of damage to the vehicle will also be added and the customer will be liable to pay in full for every damage repair to the vehicle.</li>
	<li>In case the customer fails to drop the vehicle at the drop location that is chosen by the user, a penalty charge will be levied. The customer will have to pay an amount of INR 1500 in addition to the overtime charges if any case the booking clashes with any other booking.</li>
